haar Card is a mandatory document for this scholarship. In case the candidates does not possess this ID, they must visit the nearest enrollment center and get enrolled.He / She must belong to SC / ST / OBC / Disabled Category.Any applicant must be a regular, full time student studying in any Govt. School or School run by Local Bodies.All the ID Proofs must be attached and uploaded in the prescribed format in online application form.List of Documents for AP Pre Matric Scholarship Scheme 2018-19Candidates must upload the following documents to complete the Pre Matric Scholarship Scheme Registration Process:-Income Certificate from MeeSevaCaste Certificate Obtained from MeeSevaBonafide Certificate issued by the Head of the institution (School)Aadhaar Card / UID (Scanned Copy)First Page of Bank Pass Book (Scanned Copy)All the candidates are required to complete the application process within the prescribed time duration to avail scholarship benefits. For more details, visit the official website https://jnanabhumi.ap.gov.in/  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}